# 🛍️ Ecommerce Flash Sale Website

An advanced, high-performance flash sale web application with real-time inventory management, user authentication, and secure session handling. Built using **Node.js**, **Redis**, **MongoDB**, and deployed with **Netlify + ngrok** for development.

🔗 **Live Demo**: [https://ecommerceflashsale.netlify.app/](https://ecommerceflashsale.netlify.app/)

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🧾 User registration and session-based login
- ⏱️ Real-time inventory control using **Redis**
- 🧠 Product reservation with time-based expiry
- 🔐 Access control for user and admin routes
- 📦 MongoDB integration for user and transaction data
- 🌍 Deployed frontend on **Netlify**, backend exposed using **ngrok** (during development)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Frontend**: HTML, CSS, JavaScript
- **Backend**: Node.js, Express.js
- **Database**: MongoDB
- **In-Memory Store**: Redis
- **Dev Tools**: ngrok (local backend tunneling), Netlify (frontend hosting)

---

## ⚙️ Setup Instructions

### 🔧 Pre-requisites

- Node.js & npm installed
- MongoDB running locally or Atlas
- Redis installed and running
- ngrok account (for dev backend)

---

